{"tha-ap181:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap181:0.2":"Kumudavagga ","tha-ap181:0.3":"Tikicchakattheraapadana ","tha-ap181:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap181:1.2":"vejjo asim susikkhito; ","tha-ap181:1.3":"Aturanam sadukkhanam, ","tha-ap181:1.4":"mahajanasukhavaho. ","tha-ap181:2.1":"Byadhitam samanam disva, ","tha-ap181:2.2":"silavantam mahajutim; ","tha-ap181:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap181:2.4":"bhesajjamadadim tada. ","tha-ap181:3.1":"Arogo asi teneva, ","tha-ap181:3.2":"samano samvutindriyo; ","tha-ap181:3.3":"Asoko nama namena, ","tha-ap181:3.4":"upatthako vipassino. ","tha-ap181:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap181:4.2":"yam osadhamadasaham; ","tha-ap181:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap181:4.4":"bhesajjassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap181:5.1":"Ito ca atthame kappe, ","tha-ap181:5.2":"sabbosadhasanamako; ","tha-ap181:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap181:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap181:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap181:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap181:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap181:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tikicchako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap181:8.1":"Tikicchakattherassapadanam navamam. "}